The Terrex MYSHELTER Snow 2-Layer jacket combines functionality and style for distraction-free fun on the slopes this ski season. 
 
The PrimaLoft Insulation x Parley Ocean Plastic keeps you warm on even the coldest of days, while the RAIN.RDY materials help to shield against wind and snow. The fully adjustable, helmet-compatible hood allows for extra coverage when you need it. 
 
The under-arm ventilation zips help cool you down when things heat up, while multiple pockets—including a forearm pass pocket—keep your valuables safe and easily accessible. The elastic, stretchy powder skirt also helps to keep you dry on the hill.

Little compares to the lightweight warmth of down. Zip up the adidas Essentials Down Jacket and experience it for yourself. Down baffles seal in the heat, and classic 3-Stripes style keeps it street ready. It's made of recycled materials, one important step toward reducing environmental impact.

A full embrace of alien conspiracies and desert psychedelic vibes. That's what you get with this t-shirt. The bold cactus print on the back nods to those hidden mysteries that definitely don't — but maybe just might — exist. The oval logo on the front takes its cues from old adidas catalogues.

Laid-back, casual ease is synonymous with the world of skate culture, and these sweat pants capture that exact attitude. With their soft French terry build, they're all about comfort. An expressive graphic adds a certain pop, with inspiration from the adidas archives.

There's no question that skate culture is a mix of ease and edge — in attitude and style. That simultaneously bold and laid-back aesthetic gets distilled into this adidas jacket. The green exterior has an unassuming side, with a purple interior for an unexpected pop.

The '90s were loud, experimental and unafraid. Just like these adidas Ozelia shoes. Lace in and let your inner confidence unleash as you stride through the day on shock-absorbent Adiprene cushioning. The sleek, futuristic style looks fast. But you'll want to stroll slow enough to really show them off.

This product is made with recycled content as part of our ambition to end plastic waste. 20% of pieces used to make the upper are made with minimum 50% recycled content.

description: The adidas x Wales Bonner Knit Pants are made of luxurious, deep blue knit fabric with contrasting ribbed details. They feature embroidered adidas and Wales Bonner branding in expressive orange.

Go ahead, give in to comfort. It's as easy as slipping on these adidas sweat pants when you roll out of bed in the morning. Next stop, coffee shop or couch? Either way, an art deco-inspired Trefoil decorates your look with a splash of decadence. 

By buying cotton products from us, you're supporting more sustainable cotton farming.

When you wear the Trefoil, it's more than just a style. It's a statement. A representation of adidas' sports heritage and fearless attitude. But when you wear it on this hoodie? The style factor is turned up with an art deco-inspired design. It's equal parts everyday comfort and work of art. 

By buying cotton products from us, you're supporting more sustainable cotton farming.

Go with less is more in this luxe tee from adidas. The wraparound script gives it a modern, minimalist look. A small golden Trefoil crowns the "A" for a majestic pop. Soft cotton feels decadent against your skin every time you pull it on.

By buying cotton products from us, you're supporting more sustainable cotton farming.

What do a group of aliens, an animated couch and a cactus all have in common? They're all chilling hard on this adidas t-shirt. Inspired by the world of skate, it has a laid-back look and feel with a soft cotton build and playful vibes.

Y-3 blends inspiration from its past with state-of-the-art adidas technology to introduce a new silhouette. The Qisan Cozy takes cues from the iconic Y-3 Qasa, borrowing inspiration from the heel tab to complete the slip-on design. A neoprene upper with suede and rubber detailing establishes the connection further. The TPU plate shines through the distinctive tooling.

Y-3 evolves the adidas legacy with the Y-3 GR.1P High Shoes. Crafted to reduce environmental impact, the undyed leather upper gives off a natural hint of subtle, unassuming blue. Strong statement details create a distinctive edge, balancing the worlds of performance running and style. Signature 3-Stripes and Y-3 logos detail the ultramodern look.
color: Non Dyed / Non Dyed / Core White

description:
Belonging to his father figure, Jango Fett, Star Wars™ Boba Fett's armour is legendary. Stand out and walk tall in these essential track pants inspired by the impenetrable suit – a collaboration with Disney and Lucasfilms. Wherever you roam in the galaxy, from the city to your sofa, do it in a suit that belongs to you, nobody else.
 
These exclusive track pants are only available through adidas online. You won't find them anywhere else, however hard you hunt.

Boba Fett is back, and he wants his seat. Pay homage to the moment of return Boba-style, with a hoodie that's perfect for the street or for claiming your rightful place on the sofa to watch the rest of the Star Wars™ saga, created in collaboration with Disney and Lucasfilm. 

With iconic details, elasticated cuffs and a drawstring, this statement hoodie is the ultimate in bounty hunter ease. It's only available exclusively through adidas online, you won't find it anywhere else.

description:
Jeremy Scott needs no introduction, but we'll give you one anyway. The beloved, occasionally controversial designer creates dialogue through his loud, whimsical designs. Together we explore some of his world, bringing pieces of it into our latest collection.

Nothing about the camo design of this adidas windbreaker is about blending in. Vibrant neon patches with fashion designer Jeremy Scott's artwork make that impossible. Bungee-adjustable details and a sleek, wind-blocking polyester ripstop build up your comfort level when you're on the go.

Music clears your mind, moves your body and gets you in the zone. The adidas Z.N.E. 01 earbuds offer engaging sound without ever holding you back. When it comes to comfort, these earbuds check all the boxes. They're sleek and simple, giving you an easy fit through active days. Wear them as an everyday pair or while you train. Sweat-proof and splash-proof, they stand up to everything from wet-weather commutes to quick sessions at the gym.
